Parameter Specification Technical Justification
System Designation Hypersonic Cruise Missile (HCM) Designed for high-speed atmospheric transit.
Propulsion System Scramjet (Supersonic Combustion Ramjet) Essential for maintaining stability and thrust at Mach 40.
Max Velocity Mach 40 (Approx. 13,600 m/s) Targeted velocity for rapid global reach and interceptor evasion.
Fuel Type Slush Hydrogen / High-Density Synthetic Fuel Provides high energy density and acts as a coolant for the engine.
Thermal Protection Carbon-Carbon Composite & Ablative TPS To withstand extreme aero-heating exceeding 2500°C.
Guidance System AI-Driven Adaptive Trajectory Governor Implemented in Python/C for real-time path correction and evasion.
Evasive Capability Randomized Multi-Axis Maneuvering High-G maneuvers to bypass advanced missile defense systems.
Airframe Design Waverider / Stealth-Optimized Geometry Minimizes Radar Cross Section (RCS) and maximizes lift.